headline: State Street Issues 2025 Digital Assets Outlook: Institutions Double Down on Tokenization
summary: BOSTON, October 09, 2025--State Street today published its 2025 global research on digital assets and emerging technologies, revealing a decisive shift in adoption and strategic commitment among institutional investors toward tokenization and blockchain-enabled transformation. The study, based on a global survey of senior executives across asset management and asset ownership1, captures sentiment, strategy, and operational readiness across regions and institution sizes.
